{{Infobox book series | name = Book of World Records Series | image = <!-- include the file, px and alt: [[File:Example.jpg|200px|Cover]] --> | image_caption = | books = | author = | title_orig = | translator = | illustrator = | cover_artist = | country = [[United States]] | language = | genre = | publisher = [[Scholastic Corporation|Scholastic]] | pub_date = | english_pub_date = | media_type = | number_of_books = | list_books = | preceded by = | followed by = }} The '''''Book of World Records Series''''' is a [[book series]] published once a year by [[Scholastic Corporation|Scholastic]].<ref>[http://www.scholastic.com Scholastic Website]</ref> The series was designed to inform about current [[World record|records]]. There is another world record series that outsells this one, but this one shows the top five in each category. The 2010 publication was written by Jenifer Corr Morse.
