{{Infobox book | name = Great Prince's, Tsar's and Emperor's Hunting in Russia | image = Kutepov's hunting - vol. 1.jpg | caption = | author = [[Nikolai Kutepov]] | country = [[Russian Empire]] | language = Russian | subject = | genre = | publisher = | pub_date = 1896-1911 | media_type = | pages = | isbn = | oclc = | dewey = | congress = | preceded_by = | followed_by = }}
'''Great Prince's, Tsar's and Emperor's Hunting in Russia''' ({{Lang-ru|'''Великокняжеская, царская и императорская охота на Руси'''}}) is a book by Russian historian [[Nikolai Kutepov]] published from 1896 to 1911.
== Table of contents == * ''Book One'' (1896) * ''Book Two'' (1898) * ''Book Three'' (1902) * ''Book Four'' (1911)
